            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Lerrisu begins to sing a mournful dirge that unsettles the living but bolsters her ghostly allies. Each living creature within 30 feet must attempt a @Check[will|dc:28] save with the following results, while each of her ghostly companions within 30 feet become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Quickened] until the start of Lerrisu's next turn; they can use the extra action only to Fly or Strike.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] by sadness invoked by the dirge until the start of Lerrisu's next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} by sadness.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 2}.</p>"
                },
